OL,3,CWho could replace Arne Slot as head
OL,4,Ccoach of LFC?
OL,6,FSports Correspondent Mike Hall on the
OL,7,Flikely candidates to replace Arne Slot
OL,8,Fas head coach of Liverpool FC.
OL,10,FLFC will now begin their search for a
OL,11,Fthird manager in nearly 11 years,
OL,12,Fafter outgoing head coach Arne Slot
OL,13,Fwas sacked on Saturday.
OL,15,FThe Club said they were hugely
OL,16,Fgrateful to the Dutchman, who steered
OL,17,Fthe Reds through to a Premier League
OL,18,Ftitle during his first season - but
OL,19,Fsaid it was time for "a change of
OL,20,Fdirection."
OL,26,@|D@KO]
