OL,3,CWho could replace Arne Slot as head
OL,4,Ccoach of LFC?
OL,6,FSo who could take the reins?
OL,8,FThe 43-year-old Spaniard is the clear
OL,9,Ffavourite for the job after turning
OL,10,FBournemouth into a Premier League
OL,11,Fforce. He announced in April that he
OL,12,Fwould leave the Cherries at the end of
OL,13,Fthe season and signed off in style by
OL,14,Fdelivering Europa League football for
OL,15,Fthe first time in their history. The
OL,16,Fformer Spain defender had previously
OL,17,Fwon promotion to LaLiga with his
OL,18,Fformer club Rayo Vallecano.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
