OL,3,CWho could replace Arne Slot as head
OL,4,Ccoach of LFC?
OL,6,FFormer Barcelona and Spain boss
OL,7,FEnrique is a serial major trophy
OL,8,Fwinner. The 56-year-old steered Barca
OL,9,Fto LaLiga and Champions League double
OL,10,Fin 2015 before transforming Paris St
OL,11,FGermain into the best team in Europe.
OL,12,FHe has also won three successive Ligue
OL,13,F1 crowns with the French club and
OL,14,Fshould PSG successfully defend their
OL,15,FChampions League crown he could be
OL,16,Fready for a new challenge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
