OL,3,CWho could replace Arne Slot as head
OL,4,Ccoach of LFC?
OL,6,FThe 51-year-old Austrian is another
OL,7,Ffree agent having announced in January
OL,8,Fthat he would be leaving Crystal
OL,9,FPalace at the end of the season.
OL,10,FGlasner also bowed out in style after
OL,11,Fworking wonders at Selhurst Park. The
OL,12,Fformer Eintracht Frankfurt boss led
OL,13,FPalace to their first major trophy
OL,14,Fwhen they lifted the FA Cup last
OL,15,Fseason and he signed off by guiding
OL,16,Fthem to Conference League glory this
OL,17,Fweek for their first European trophy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
