OL,3,CWho could replace Arne Slot as head
OL,4,Ccoach of LFC?
OL,6,FShould the Anfield hierarchy want
OL,7,Fanother German head coach following
OL,8,Fthe success under Jurgen Klopp,
OL,9,FStuttgart's 44-year-old Hoeness, the
OL,10,Fnephew of Germany great Uli Hoeness,
OL,11,Fcould be the answer. He led Bayern
OL,12,FMunich II to the Bundesliga 3 title in
OL,13,F2020 before galvanising his current
OL,14,Fclub, who he transformed from top-
OL,15,Fflight relegation battlers into a
OL,16,FChampions League side and DFB-Pokal
OL,17,Fwinners in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
