OL,3,CWho could replace Arne Slot as head
OL,4,Ccoach of LFC?
OL,6,FLiverpool icon Gerrard would be a
OL,7,Frisky choice given his disappointing
OL,8,Fspell in charge of Aston Villa, but he
OL,9,Fis revered by the Anfield club's
OL,10,Ffanbase. The 46-year-old also led
OL,11,FRangers to the Scottish Premiership
OL,12,Ftitle in 2021 without losing a league
OL,13,Fmatch and has since gained further
OL,14,Fmanagerial experience following a
OL,15,Fstint in charge of Saudi Pro League
OL,16,Fclub Al-Ettifaq, who he left by mutual
OL,17,Fconsent in early 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
